{
  "texts": [
    "The depot shall be launched and brought to its final orbit in an empty or partially filled state, since its wet mass might exceed the capacities of available launchers.",
    "Propellant transfer from a tanker to the depot and from the depot to an exploration spacecraft is required.",
    "Depots have multiple advantages:",
    "The dry mass of an exploration payload, launched from the surface of the Earth, may be larger, because it will be fueled in space. 2.",
    "Commercial launch services can be used to supply and re-supply the depot. 3."
  ]
}